sequenceDiagram
    actor Customer
    participant Home
    participant Login
    participant API
    participant Auth
    participant Storage
    participant Tab
    participant Room
    participant Admin

    Customer->>Home: Tap Sign In
    Home->>Login: Present sheet
    Customer->>Login: Submit email + OTP
    Login->>API: Send login request
    API-->>Login: user + mock token
    Login->>Auth: set currentUser + isAuthenticated
    Auth->>Storage: persist token and user fields
    Auth-->>Home: authenticated state
    Customer->>Tab: Open Live Tab
    Tab->>API: Start session
    Tab->>Room: Subscribe to session room
    Admin->>API: Separate unauthenticated proxy requests
    Note over API,Admin: Customer auth is mocked. Admin access stays on a separate server surface.
